artifacts.name: godbook.jar
artifacts.description: Helps you time godbooking by showing which tick other players preached on

artifacts.name: playerstatusextended.jar
artifacts.description: Tells you if other players who also have this plugin are swinging unpotted, and tells them if you are. You can only see it for other people who also have this plugin.

artifacts.name: socketping.jar
artifacts.description: SOCKET MUST BE INSTALLED OR THIS WILL NOT INSTALL. Useless plugin. Ctrl+Click to mark a tile for other players who also have this plugin to see.

artifacts.name: SocketDeathIndicators.jar
artifacts.description: SOCKET MUST BE INSTALLED OR THIS WILL NOT INSTALL. Hides Nylos that have been killed by projectile that is still in the air. Only shows other players' kills who also have this plugin.

artifacts.name: socketplayerindicators.jar
artifacts.description: SOCKET MUST BE INSTALLED OR THIS WILL NOT INSTALL. Just like standard player indicators plugin except for people who are in the same socket as you. Useful for finding those private off players you raid with.

artifacts.name: csotetseg.jar
artifacts.description: SOCKET MUST BE INSTALLED OR THIS WILL NOT INSTALL. Shows you the solved maze. Does not work in solos, maze time isn't accurate when chosen.

artifacts.name: cChatExtensions.jar
artifacts.description: Allows you to ctrl+v into chat box.

artifacts.name: sChat.jar
artifacts.description: SOCKET MUST BE INSTALLED OR THIS WILL NOT INSTALL. Allows you to chat via socket.
